  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An anomaly-finding horror game, but the rules of survival constantly change. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Average Play Time: 120-240 minutes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mark five differences from the camera footage in each room to complete it.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/050cdb68d1eb0f572667dce15591e651.poster.avif?t=1754601320\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/050cdb68d1eb0f572667dce15591e651.webm?t=1754601320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/050cdb68d1eb0f572667dce15591e651.mp4?t=1754601320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive your stepfamily members and toys by figuring out their patterns and rules.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/90eed2e7036affdf92f06c0642daea6f.poster.avif?t=1754601320\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/90eed2e7036affdf92f06c0642daea6f.webm?t=1754601320\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163730/extras/90eed2e7036affdf92f06c0642daea6f.mp4?t=1754601320\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
